AI Content Detector â€“ Mini Project 3

A Web Application for AI vs Human Authorship Verification

This project is a web application built using ReactJS (frontend) and Python (backend). It detects whether a given text/prompt is authored by a human or generated by an AI model.
The application was designed to participate in the Voight-Kampff Generative AI Authorship Verification 2024 challenge.

