âš™ï¸ Algorithm & Workflow

The detection logic relies on Perplexity and Burstiness computed using GPT-2:

Perplexity (PPL):

Measures how well the model predicts text.

Lower PPL â†’ Text is more predictable â†’ Likely AI.

Higher PPL â†’ Text is less predictable â†’ Likely human.

Burstiness:

Measures variation in PPL across sentences.

High variation â†’ Indicates AI-like patterns.

Thresholding for Decision:

PPL < 60 â†’ AI-generated

60 â‰¤ PPL < 80 â†’ Most likely AI (needs more text)

PPL â‰¥ 80 â†’ Human-written

API Endpoint:

POST / â†’ Accepts JSON { "text": "..." }

Returns { "label": "AI-generated/Human-written", "perplexity": ..., "burstiness": ... }

