ğŸ“Š Evaluation Metrics

Perplexity (PPL):

Low â†’ More predictable â†’ AI-like.

High â†’ More diverse â†’ Human-like.

Burstiness:

High â†’ Indicates unusual variance â†’ AI.

Low â†’ Consistent â†’ Human.

